g.text: No. All games were outlawed in the Great Martian War of 17380.

g.text: Yeah, well, your questions are obnoxious.

g.text: I really only had board games. And by that... I mean I really only had one board game.

g.text: I don't have a favorite. I'm not very good at games.

g.text: aww! do you wanna learn? i can teach you.
